thread.title: BRIEF-Anadolu Anonim Turk FY 2017 Net Profit Jumps To 201.5 Mln Lira

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Anadolu Anonim Turk FY 2017 Net Profit Jumps To 201.5 Mln Lira
text:
Jan 30 (Reuters) - ANADOLU ANONIM TURK SIGORTA:
* REPORTED ON MONDAY FY 2017 CONSOLIDATED NET PROFIT OF 201.5 MILLION LIRA VS 102.1 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 CONSOLIDATED NON-LIFE TECHNICAL INCOME OF 3.91 BILLION LIRA VS 3.57 BILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
